Searching for James Meredith in the Baruch Ticker turns an editorial on page 3 of the November 20, 1962 issue.

samplefilepath <- tempfile("sample.pdf")
download.file('http://ticker.baruch.cuny.edu/files/articles/ticker_19621120.pdf', samplefilepath, mode='wb')
page <- pdf_render_page(samplefilepath, page = 3)
png::writePNG(page, 'page.png')
knitr::include_graphics('page.png')
